State
v.
Jones 2018-0444 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 27, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellee/cross-appellant's motion for leave to file delayed cross-appeal. Motion granted. Appellee/cross-appellant shall file a memorandum in support of jurisdiction within 30 days.

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, J., dissent. DeGenaro, J., not participating.
